What kind of visual information do you expect to find?
Some graphical cues to aim the hand (a cursor would be helpful). Also a profile view would help to know the height from the hand to the board.

Not at all
Extremely
What kind of tactile information do you expect to sense through the haptic when the robot is grasping the chip?
Just the "scaled" weight of the chip.

A virtual wall to know that the arm is touching the table.
